name: A childhood memory
description: You are a kid in the passenger seat. Driving past a windmill. All of your worries were just a dream and it's already fading away. You just enjoy the view, the butterflies and the distant music. You wonder if the driver in the pink car has any worries. But you do not hold onto that feeling for long, because you are just enjoying the view.   Music : With Some Malice - Francesco D'Andrea
